# RateRadar — Project Overview

## What is this?
A single-page application that aggregates and displays global data in one place.
Three tabs: Fuel Prices, Currency Rates, Food Basket Index.

## Data Source
OpenVan.camp Public API — free, no auth, CORS enabled, CC BY 4.0.
- Fuel: GET https://openvan.camp/api/fuel/prices
- Currency: GET https://openvan.camp/api/currency/rates
- Basket: GET https://openvan.camp/api/vanbasket/countries
- Always append ?source=radar.viredsoft.com to every API call.

## Hosting
Static SPA — built with Vite, deployed via FTP to shared hosting.
Domain: radar.viredsoft.com

## Stack
- Vue 3 + TypeScript
- Vite 8
- Tailwind CSS v4
- Vue Router 5
- Pinia 3
- Chart.js + vue-chartjs

## Project Structure
src/
  components/     # shared UI components
  views/          # FuelView, CurrencyView, BasketView
  stores/         # Pinia stores per feature
  composables/    # reusable logic
  types/          # TypeScript interfaces
  router/         # Vue Router config

## Attribution
Every page must show in the footer:
"Data source: OpenVan.camp (CC BY 4.0)"